package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/KlugerLab/FIt-SNE/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:

    - command -v fast_tsne

  license: Multiple
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  license_family: OTHER
  summary: Fast Fourier Transform-accelerated Interpolation-based t-SNE (FIt-SNE)

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - raivivek
    - dkobak
    - linqiaozhi
